---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/docs-layout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Changelog — Mekong CLI" description="Full version history for Mekong CLI. Every release, feature, improvement, and fix documented with dates and badges.">
  <article class="changelog" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem">
    <h1 class="gradient-text">Changelog</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);margin-bottom:3rem">Every release, every change. Updated with each version of Mekong CLI.</p>

    <!-- v5.0 -->
    <div class="release" style="margin-bottom:3rem;padding-bottom:3rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--md-sys-color-outline)">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">
        <h2 style="margin:0">v5.0.0</h2>
        <span class="badge badge-current">Current</span>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);margin-bottom:1.5rem">March 21, 2026</p>
      <ul class="change-list">
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>OpenClaw Engine</strong> — full PEV (Plan-Execute-Verify) loop with autonomous rollback on failed verification gates</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>319 commands</strong> across 5 layers: Founder, Business, Product, Engineering, Ops — up from 230 in v4.5</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>MCU billing system</strong> — credit-based pricing deducted only on successful delivery; HTTP 402 on zero balance</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Universal LLM routing</strong> — 3-variable config supports any provider: OpenRouter, Anthropic, Qwen, Gemini, DeepSeek, Ollama</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>RaaS API v2</strong> — REST endpoint for all 319 commands; async mission dispatch with webhook delivery</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Tôm Hùm daemon</strong> — autonomous CTO mode running continuous Plan→Deploy→Verify→Status loop</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>542 skill definitions</strong> in <code>.claude/skills/</code> — auto-loaded on session start</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>mekong cook</strong> — now generates tests by default, verifies build before reporting success</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>Provider fallback chain</strong> — automatic failover across 7 providers when primary is unavailable</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> Session context loss on long-running missions exceeding 32k tokens</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> Pre-commit hook false positives on files containing the word "apps" in comments</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- v4.5 -->
    <div class="release" style="margin-bottom:3rem;padding-bottom:3rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--md-sys-color-outline)">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">
        <h2 style="margin:0">v4.5.0</h2>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);margin-bottom:1.5rem">January 15, 2026</p>
      <ul class="change-list">
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Founder layer commands</strong> — 46 commands: <code>annual</code>, <code>okr</code>, <code>fundraise</code>, <code>swot</code>, <code>pitch</code>, <code>vc/cap-table</code>, <code>ipo/*</code></li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>230 commands total</strong> — major expansion of sales, marketing, and finance command sets</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Cloudflare-only deploy infrastructure</strong> — 3-layer scaffold: Pages + Workers + D1/KV/R2</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>410 machine contracts</strong> in <code>factory/contracts/</code> — JSON-defined agent workflows</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>mekong sales/prospect</strong> — now enriches with LinkedIn data and ICP scoring in single pass</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>mekong review</strong> — security scan now covers OWASP Top 10, not just TypeScript errors</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> Shell init script — <code>source shell-init.sh</code> now sets up all provider aliases in under 1 second</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> <code>mekong-qwen</code> alias failing when <code>DASHSCOPE_API_KEY</code> not set in environment</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> Race condition in parallel agent execution when writing to shared <code>.mekong/tasks/</code> directory</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- v4.0 -->
    <div class="release" style="margin-bottom:3rem;padding-bottom:3rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--md-sys-color-outline)">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">
        <h2 style="margin:0">v4.0.0</h2>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);margin-bottom:1.5rem">October 3, 2025</p>
      <ul class="change-list">
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Multi-provider architecture</strong> — single <code>mekong</code> binary routes to Claude, Gemini, Qwen, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Agent layer</strong> — <code>GitAgent</code>, <code>FileAgent</code>, <code>ShellAgent</code>, <code>LeadHunter</code>, <code>ContentWriter</code> as composable primitives</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>mekong-docs</strong> package — Astro-based documentation site with guides, API reference, and blog</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>PEV Engine</strong> — <code>planner.py</code>, <code>executor.py</code>, <code>verifier.py</code>, <code>orchestrator.py</code> replacing monolithic task runner</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>LLM client</strong> — unified <code>llm_client.py</code> with automatic retry and provider health checks</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> <strong>mekong deploy</strong> — now validates Cloudflare Workers syntax before pushing; rolls back on health check failure</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> <code>mekong test</code> hanging indefinitely when pytest subprocess produced no output for 60+ seconds</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> Incorrect MCU deduction when mission was partially executed before provider timeout</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> <code>mekong status</code> showing stale task state when <code>.mekong/tasks/</code> was modified externally</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- v3.0 -->
    <div class="release" style="margin-bottom:3rem">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">
        <h2 style="margin:0">v3.0.0</h2>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);margin-bottom:1.5rem">June 12, 2025</p>
      <ul class="change-list">
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Initial public release</strong> — Mekong CLI open-sourced under MIT license</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>135 commands</strong> across Engineering and Ops layers</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>CC CLI integration</strong> — <code>mekong</code> wrapper delegates to Claude Code CLI with full command discovery</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>Skill system</strong> — 200+ skill definitions in <code>.claude/skills/</code> covering code, research, and business operations</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>mekong cook</strong> — natural language to production code with plan, execute, verify loop</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-new">New</span> <strong>mekong fix</strong> — AI-powered bug resolution with full codebase context</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-improved">Improved</span> Command discovery — commands in <code>.claude/commands/</code> auto-loaded without symlinks or manual registration</li>
        <li><span class="badge badge-fixed">Fixed</span> Shell init script failing on zsh when <code>~/.zshrc</code> used non-standard <code>PATH</code> ordering</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div style="padding:2rem;background:var(--md-sys-color-surface-container);border-radius:12px;text-align:center">
      <h3>Stay Up to Date</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)">Follow the repo on GitHub for release notifications. New versions ship monthly.</p>
      <md-elevated-button onclick="location.href='/'">Get Started Free</md-elevated-button>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00bcd4, #0097a7);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .release h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
  }
  .change-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .change-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--md-sys-color-surface-container);
    color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .change-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .badge-current { background: #00bcd4; color: #fff; }
  .badge-new { background: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.15); color: #00bcd4; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.3); }
  .badge-improved { background: rgba(103, 80, 164, 0.15); color: #9c7df5; border: 1px solid rgba(103, 80, 164, 0.3); }
  .badge-fixed { background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.15); color: #66bb6a; border: 1px solid rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3); }
  code {
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
    background: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1);
    padding: 2px 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
</style>
